"The default model is ``Qwen/Qwen3-14B``.  For gated models (e.g., Llama),"
" create a Secret with your Hugging Face token:"
msgstr "默认模型是 ``Qwen/Qwen3-14B``\\ 。对于受限模型（例如 Llama），请使用您的 Hugging Face Token 创建一个 Secret："

#: ../../source/mp/deployment.rst:105
msgid "Then add the ``HF_TOKEN`` environment variable to the vLLM container spec."
msgstr "然后将 ``HF_TOKEN`` 环境变量添加到 vLLM 容器规格中。"

#: ../../source/mp/deployment.rst:107
msgid "**Step 4: Monitor deployment**"
msgstr "**步骤 4：监控部署**"

#: ../../source/mp/deployment.rst:126
